data.description: Introducing 1320 Chesapeake Drive - A Captivating Waterfront Retreat Experience the epitome of luxury living at this magnificent 3-story masterpiece, offering unparalleled 180-degree views of the pristine Chesapeake Bay. Nestled in the heart of serene coastal beauty, this exquisite home has been thoughtfully remodeled from top to bottom, boasting the highest quality finishes and unmatched attention to detail. Unmatched Water Views! Wake up to the breathtaking beauty of the Chesapeake Bay each morning, as this home provides unobstructed, panoramic vistas from every floor. Watch the sunrise over the tranquil waters from your private decks, and savor the serenity of waterfront living.  With three meticulously designed levels, this home offers a perfect blend of space and sophistication. Each level features its own private deck, providing a seamless indoor-outdoor living experience and enhancing the captivating water views. The kitchen features an Electrolux Fridge, LG appliances, a stove with Bluetooth compatibility with convection features and a cafe white dishwasher.  No expense was spared in the complete renovation of this home. From the moment you step inside, you'll be enveloped in the finest materials and craftsmanship. Every corner of this residence exudes opulence, making it a true sanctuary of luxury. The entire third floor is dedicated to a lavish primary suite. Escape to your personal haven of comfort, featuring a spacious bedroom, a spa-like en-suite bathroom, and, of course, a private deck where you can unwind while gazing at the ever-changing waters of the Chesapeake Bay. The tankless water heater (2022) is just one more item the seller insured was installed to create the luxurious feel of the home. This is a rare opportunity to own a home where luxury meets nature, where tranquility meets elegance. 1320 Chesapeake Drive is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle that will leave you in awe every single day. If you seek the finest in coastal living and a retreat that redefines luxury, this is the address you've been waiting for. Discover the magic of the Chesapeake Bay living and make this waterfront masterpiece your own. Schedule your private tour today and embark on the journey to make this dream home a reality. Don't miss your chance to experience life on the Chesapeake Bay like never before. The neighborhood boasts private marinas, volleyball, small beaches to kyack and paddleboard, swim, and much more.
